  "title": "Retail Assistant/ Retail Sales [Sports/ Fashion/ Footwear] - 5 Days Work",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Multiple Location</p></li><li><p>Great career progression</p></li><li><p>Training provided</p></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Provide Excellent Customer Service:</strong> Greet and assist customers professionally, understand their needs, recommend suitable products, and resolve inquiries or issues promptly.</p></li><li><p><strong>Drive Sales Performance:</strong> Collaborate with team members to achieve sales targets, demonstrate product features and benefits effectively, and stay informed about product knowledge and industry trends.</p></li><li><p><strong>Process Transactions:</strong> Accurately and efficiently handle sales transactions using POS systems.</p></li><li><p><strong>Maintain Store Presentation:</strong> Assist with merchandising, visual displays, and ensure the store remains clean, organized, and welcoming.</p></li><li><p><strong>Manage Inventory:</strong> Monitor stock levels and replenish inventory as needed to support smooth operations.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Candidates with <strong>Sales or Retail </strong>experience are welcome to apply</p></li></ul><p><br /><br />To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Boo Seng Hong (R25129172)</p>",
